OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772806277
OL,3,CMan arrested in connection with
OL,4,Cterrorism offence in Eastbourne
OL,6,FA man has been arrested in connection
OL,7,Fwith a terrorism offence in Eastbourne.
OL,9,FCounter Terrorism police were called
OL,10,Fto the town on Friday morning. (6
OL,11,FMarch)
OL,13,FOfficers say a 35-year-old man from
OL,14,Fthe town was arrested on suspicion of
OL,15,Fexpressing an opinion in support of a
OL,16,Fproscribed organisation (Daesh), and
OL,17,Fis currently in police custody.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
