OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772806277
OL,3,CMan arrested in connection with
OL,4,Cterrorism offence in Eastbourne
OL,6,FThe arrest is in connection with an
OL,7,FIslamist Terrorism investigation
OL,8,Frelated to posts made on social media
OL,9,Fplatforms.
OL,11,FA search of a property in the town is
OL,12,Fongoing.
OL,14,FCh Supt Justin Burtenshaw, of Sussex
OL,15,FPolice, said: "I appreciate arrests of
OL,16,Fthis nature can cause people in the
OL,17,Flocal community to feel unsettled
OL,18,Fhowever Sussex Police has been working
OL,19,Fclosely to support our colleagues in
OL,20,FCounter Terrorism Policing South East
OL,21,Fas part of this pre-planned operation.
OL,26,@wD@OOU
