OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772806277
OL,3,CMan arrested in connection with
OL,4,Cterrorism offence in Eastbourne
OL,6,F"There is not believed to be any
OL,7,Fimmediate risk to those in the
OL,8,Fcommunity but I would urge anyone who
OL,9,Fhas any concerns to contact police.
OL,11,F"Anyone who sees or hears something
OL,12,Fthat could be terrorist-related should
OL,13,Fcall the UK Anti-Terrorist Hotline on
OL,14,F0800 789 321. In an emergency, always
OL,15,Fdial 999. "
